AI is revolutionizing how we understand and utilize data in education, transforming raw information from Learning Management Systems (LMS) and Learning Record Stores (LRS) into actionable insights that improve learning outcomes. Here's a breakdown of how AI is used for data analysis in learning, with a focus on educational data mining, data visualization, and learning analytics:
